# Build output.
#
# `site/` is COMMITTED by default so the repo is browsable the instant you clone
# it — open site/index.html, no build, no Python, no server. That is the whole
# offline-first promise, so it ships built.
#
# If you would rather keep generated HTML out of git (regenerate with
# `python3 build.py`), uncomment the next line:
# site/
